[man shouts command]

22
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:36,283
- [whispering]
- [grunting resumes]

23
00:03:36,283 --> 00:03:38,318
[blades clacking]

24
00:03:39,486 --> 00:03:41,054
[man shouts command]

25
00:04:40,414 --> 00:04:42,349
