204
00:43:48,261 --> 00:43:49,530
Please tell Lady Kiku

205
00:43:49,530 --> 00:43:52,032
I don't have the words
to thank her.

206
00:44:02,209 --> 00:44:04,711
She is honored.

207
00:46:28,789 --> 00:46:31,024
[chuckles softly]

